    &kp TAB         &ht_left LCMD A  &ht_left LALT R  &ht_left LSHFT S  &ht_left LCTRL T  &kp G     &kp M  &ht_right RCTRL N  &ht_right RSHFT E  &ht_right LALT I  &ht_right RCMD O  &kp DEL
