&none  &home_dir  &none     &kp HASH   &move_line_down  &mc_add_below      &code_blk  &kp EQUAL    &kp LBRC  &kp RBRC  &kp AT     &kp FSLH
                                       &none  &trans     &trans            &trans   &trans
            >;
